-Okay.

351
00:27:14.267 --> 00:27:16.030
Come on. come on.

352
00:27:17.604 --> 00:27:19.003
Watch your back! Look out.

353
00:27:19.205 --> 00:27:21.230
Here it is. Here's a cave. Come on.

354
00:27:21.441 --> 00:27:24.342
Right here. right here.
Go. go. go.

355
00:27:24.544 --> 00:27:25.772
Go ahead. Get in.

356
00:27:25.979 --> 00:27:27.844
Hurry. hurry. hurry.

357
00:27:31.451 --> 00:27:35.217
