454
00:35:34.467 --> 00:35:36.560
We'd like to retire
and maintain our lifestyle...

455
00:35:36.769 --> 00:35:38.202
...without paying a lot of taxes.

456
00:35:38.404 --> 00:35:41.896
So basically. you want nobody's hands
in your pockets but your own?

457
00:35:42.508 --> 00:35:44.408
Are you familiar with
tax-free municipal...?

458
00:35:44.610 --> 00:35:46.510
<i>I learned to finish my work quickly.</i>

459
00:35:46.812 --> 00:35:49.007
<i>I had to finish quickly.</i>

460
00:35:49.348 --> 00:35:52.840
<i>To get in line at Glide by 5.</i>

461
00:35:56.555 --> 00:35:58.489
Come on.

462
00:35:58.958 --> 00:36:00.550
Come on.

463
